{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_03_03",
  "title": "fran 3話 真似しないスタイル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あった！\nラッキー、まだ一つだけ残ってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ found it!\nLucky‚ there was just only one left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子のグッズってほとんどがサニピに入ってからので\nソロ時代のは、もうネットでも売ってなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Most of Haruko's goods are from Sunny Peace days‚\nso her solo era items aren't available even online anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.899987793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、遙子さんのファンだったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san‚ were you a fan of Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピより前の、ソロ時代の遙子の動画も観ましたけど\n正直、冴えないもいいとこでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before Sunny Peace‚ I watched some of her solo era videos‚\nbut honestly‚ they weren't that great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、グッズだけは凝っててセンスが良かったので\n現物を見てみたかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But her goods were unique and had a sense of style‚\nso I wanted to see them in person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そう言えば昔、遙子さんにグッズのことを相談されて）\n（一緒に考えたことがあったっけ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Come to think of it‚ Haruko-san consulted me about her goods before.）\n（We've had discussions about them together…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら遙子さんに直接頼めば良かったのでは？\n多分まだ一通り持ってると思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then it would have been better to ask Haruko-san directly‚ wouldn't it?\nShe might still have one set.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、借り物を分解する訳にはいかないでしょ\nそのくらいは自分で買いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ I can't dismantle borrowed items.\nI'll buy them myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……なんか、俺一人で勘違いしてたみたいですね\nてっきり麻奈に興味があるものだとばかり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I misunderstood on my own.\nI thought you were interested in Mana…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬麻奈ねぇ\nすずに借りた資料も見ましたけど、正直……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… Well‚ Mana Nagase.\nI saw the materials I borrowed from Suzu‚ but honestly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、{user}さんに言うことでもないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not something to tell you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "別に、何を言っても怒りはしませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. I won't get mad no matter what you say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　基本給を下げたり\nイベントのギャラから余計にピンハネしたりしません？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? You won't cut my basic salary or\ntake more from event profits?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "しません、っていうか今もしてません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm not‚ I haven't done that before either!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ言いますけど\n正直、普通でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll say it.\nHonestly‚ she was ordinary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "歌はうまかったですし、才能もあるとは思いましたよ\nでも、そこまで騒ぐほどかというと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She sang well‚ and I thought she had talent‚\nbut I don't know she was great to the point where people make such a fuss on her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ああでも、活動期間あまり長くなかったんでしたっけ\n新人と考えれば、かなりいい線いってる方だったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ her career wasn't that long.\nConsidering she was a rookie‚ she was quite decent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "あと、飾らない感じが良かったですね\n人気出そうなキャラなのはなんとなく分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I liked her natural feeling.\nI understand she was a character who could gain popularity to some extent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、でも……下手じゃないですけど\nあれなら、今のサニピの方が凄くないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ but… It wasn't bad‚\nbut isn't Sunny Peace now much better than that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "franさん\nそんなにサニピを買ってくれてたんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san.\nI didn't know you would evaluate Sunny Peace so high.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.4999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "それが客観的な評価だと思うだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's just an objective evaluation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "私達だって元BIG4ですよ\n他の子達の実力くらい、見たら分かりますって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were also former BIG4 members.\nWe can understand the abilities of other girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "でもmihoなんか、いまだに執念燃やしてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But miho still burns with passion‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "何年経っても、{user}さんにあれだけ\n長々と語らせるくらいの力はあったんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "even after all these years‚\nI had the power to talk for so long‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.6140039445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.4999989828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "話が長くて、本当にすみませんでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for making you talk so much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.3666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "確かに長瀬麻奈って人は\n『何か』鮮烈な印象を残すだけのものを持っていて",
      "translations": {
